# The Global Beautybar — environment variables
# Copy to .env (NOT committed) for local dev, or set via `vercel env add`
# for production. Used by /api/_cal.js + downstream proxy handlers.

# ---- Cal.com (REQUIRED for booking) -----------------------------------
# Create an API key at https://cal.com/settings/developer/api-keys.
# Each Cal.com event type's `slug` MUST match the keys in SERVICES
# (js/main.js) — see README for the slug list.
CALCOM_API_KEY=
